snippet.title: Action 69 - Super Bandonio Bros Gameplay (Update 8)
snippet.description:
Here is a video showcasing the upcoming Action 69 Update 8.

This video shows off what I have been working on in the past year, I am excited to show some footage of the game at this stage. Keep in mind this is still a developmental build, so this is not the final build of the game. Bugs may persist and stability issues can occur playing the build.

 In the next video, I may show off the skin shop or show some footage of the Cheetahmen Trilogy!
